  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK903">
<l>illāḷkaṭ ṭāḻnta viyalpiṉmai yeññāṉṟum </l>
<l>nallāru ṇāṇut tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The frailty that stoops to a wife will always make (her husband) feel ashamed among the good.</l>
            </lg>
